VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'watching this video. So, in this video, I\'m going to do a deep dive on Cling 2.0. I\'m going to show you all the cool things you can do, plus compare it with some other leading video generators. And I\'m also going to show you some'

[00:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'limitations of it. It\'s still not perfect, but it\'s pretty damn impressive. So, after some days of early testing, here\'s what Cling 2.0 is really good at. It\'s especially good for highaction movements, complex scenes,'

[00:38] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'camera control, and following your prompt. And honestly, the most impressive feature about Cling 2.0 is its image to video feature. This is where you can upload an image as the'

[00:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'start frame of the video. Note that version 2.0 0 currently does not support using an image as the end frame, only the start frame. I\'ll also go over text to video in a second where you just'

